modules.description: Provides string-based version and copyright information. Works with plain text data to expose software release details. Used to display build-specific identifiers in logs and user-facing outputs.

Provides string-based version and copyright information, enabling retrieval of software release details from plain text data. Exposes build-specific identifiers for use in logs and user-facing outputs. Supports operations like extracting and formatting version strings. Can be used to display licensing terms or track software revisions in runtime outputs.
